        "description": "",
        "custom_html": "<style>\n  .since-hero {\n    position: relative;\n    min-height: 80vh;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    background: #0a0a0a;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 120px 24px 80px;\n  }\n  .since-hero__bg {\n    position: absolute;\n    inset: 0;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1215 50%, #0a0a0a 100%);\n  }\n  .since-hero__particles {\n    position: absolute;\n    inset: 0;\n    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(183,0,44,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(183,0,44,0.04) 0%, transparent 40%);\n  }\n  .since-hero__content {\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 2;\n    max-width: 800px;\n  }\n  .since-hero__year {\n    font-size: clamp(80px, 15vw, 180px);\n    font-weight: 200;\n    letter-spacing: -4px;\n    line-height: 1;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\n    margin-bottom: -30px;\n    font-family: serif;\n  }\n  .since-hero__label {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 6px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #B7002C;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n  .since-hero__title {\n    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);\n    font-weight: 300;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    color: #fff;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    font-family: serif;\n  }\n  .since-hero__title strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .since-hero__sub {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    line-height: 1.8;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .since-hero__line {\n    width: 1px;\n    height: 60px;\n    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #B7002C, transparent);\n    margin: 40px auto 0;\n    animation: pulse-line 2s ease-in-out infinite;\n  }\n  @keyframes pulse-line {\n    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }\n    50% { opacity: 1; }\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n    .since-hero { min-height: 60vh; padding: 100px 20px 60px; }\n    .since-hero__year { margin-bottom: -15px; }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"since-hero\">\n  <div class=\"since-hero__bg\"></div>\n  <div class=\"since-hero__particles\"></div>\n  <div class=\"since-hero__content\">\n    <div class=\"since-hero__year\">1992</div>\n    <p class=\"since-hero__label\">Since 1992</p>\n    <h1 class=\"since-hero__title\">Three Decades of<br><strong>Skin Knowledge</strong></h1>\n    <p class=\"since-hero__sub\">From a Swiss-inspired laboratory in Miami to skincare professionals across the Americas. The Dermaswiss story is one of science, passion, and purpose.</p>\n    <div class=\"since-hero__line\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "padding_top": 0,
