        "description": "",
        "custom_html": "<style>\n  .pillars {\n    padding: 80px 24px;\n    background: #faf9f7;\n  }\n  .pillars__title {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #B7002C;\n    margin-bottom: 48px;\n  }\n  .pillars__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 32px;\n    max-width: 960px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .pillar {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 40px 24px;\n    border: 1px solid #e8e0d8;\n    background: #fff;\n    transition: all 0.4s ease;\n  }\n  .pillar:hover {\n    border-color: #B7002C;\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(183,0,44,0.06);\n    transform: translateY(-4px);\n  }\n  .pillar__icon {\n    font-size: 32px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n  .pillar__name {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #222;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .pillar__text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    line-height: 1.8;\n    color: #888;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n    .pillars__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"pillars\">\n  <p class=\"pillars__title\">The Dermaswiss Ecosystem</p>\n  <div class=\"pillars__grid\">\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar__icon\">&#9883;</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar__name\">Dermaswiss Pro</div>\n      <p class=\"pillar__text\">Professional-grade skincare for licensed estheticians. Advanced formulations, wholesale pricing, and exclusive tools for treatment rooms.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar__icon\">&#9733;</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar__name\">Education</div>\n      <p class=\"pillar__text\">Licensed esthetics programs, on-demand seminars, and continuous professional development. From student to expert, we're with you.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar__icon\">&#10084;</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar__name\">Dermaswiss</div>\n      <p class=\"pillar__text\">High-performance at-home skincare for everyone. Clean, multifunctional formulas designed for visible results from day one.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "padding_top": 0,
